Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Bohol School of Arts and Trades in Tagbilaran City to Dr. Nemesio Agunod School of Arts and Trades
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 342
An Act Changing the Name of the Bohol School of Arts and Trades in Tagbilaran City to Dr. Nemesio Agunod School of Arts and Trades
Section 1. The name of the Bohol School of Arts and Trades in Tagbilaran City is changed to Dr. Nemesio Agunod School of Arts and Trades.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: February 25, 1983
